 @* ----- Conditional Rendering ----- *@
                                    Loyalty discount @* Renders part of the basket page markup. *@
                                </span> @* Closes the matching HTML element. *@
 @* ----- Card Layout ----- *@
                                <span class="bk-summary__row-value" style="color:var(--text-light);font-weight:500;">—</span> @* Renders inline text or badge content. *@
                            </div> @* Closes the matching HTML element. *@
                            <div class="bk-summary__row" style="border-bottom:none;padding-top:4px;"> @* Starts a layout container for this section. *@
 @* ----- Form Fields ----- *@
                                <span class="bk-summary__row-label" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:12px;"> @* Renders inline text or badge content. *@
                                    <i data-lucide="salad" style="width:13px;height:13px;stroke-width:2;color:var(--text-light)"></i> @* Renders part of the basket page markup. *@
                                    Add broccoli, carrot &amp; apple for 10% off @* Renders part of the basket page markup. *@
                                </span> @* Closes the matching HTML element. *@
                            </div> @* Closes the matching HTML element. *@
